nurbsCurve.py
	Plot a nurbs curve with control points positioned on a circle. The
	deviation from a real circle is visualised by rotating the curve
	about its center.
	Simply position your mouse pointer on the curve and notice the 
	deviation while the object is rotating.

nurbsCircle.py
	Plot a circle using NURBS and control points connected by lines.
	See Foley, van Dam, Feiner, Hughes: "Computer Graphics",
	second edition in C, Chapter 11.2.3, Fig. 11.31 
	Do the test with the mouse pointer again ...
